content: Yes, I can help you with that! Pod 51 Hotel offers a continental breakfast for an additional fee, and The Bowery House offers a complimentary breakfast buffet. The Jane Hotel and The Local Hostel do not provide breakfast, but they have their restaurant/café where you can purchase food. Finally, The Hotel Newton offers a free coffee and tea service. Keep in mind that the complimentary breakfast or coffee service might have changed due to the COVID-19 pandemic.
